summary: Adventurous language enthusiast passionate about fostering global connections. Experienced in supply chain, customer relations, and project management. Skilled in operations, logistics, and product development. Currently driving successful outcomes in the fast-paced agricultural trading industry. Thrives in multifaceted roles, solving problems with a customer-centric mindset. Continuous learner, constantly seeking new adventures.
